01:11:22.960 --> 01:11:25.660 align:middle line:90%
But at that time, it was like--

01:11:25.660 --> 01:11:30.170 align:middle line:84%
and that we have enough
money to get groceries and--

01:11:30.170 --> 01:11:33.250 align:middle line:84%
at that time, we were
just barely getting

01:11:33.250 --> 01:11:37.850 align:middle line:90%
by with our finances.

01:11:37.850 --> 01:11:40.600 align:middle line:90%
But I was just so--

01:11:40.600 --> 01:11:44.110 align:middle line:90%
I realized I was content.

01:11:44.110 --> 01:11:46.540 align:middle line:84%
So I think contentment
and fulfillment

01:11:46.540 --> 01:11:49.490 align:middle line:90%
are two sides of the same coin.

01:11:49.490 --> 01:11:53.030 align:middle line:84%
And I learned-- cancer taught
me gratitude and contentment,

01:11:53.030 --> 01:11:55.520 align:middle line:84%
two things I'd never
understood before.

01:11:55.520 --> 01:11:58.210 align:middle line:84%
And I realized, if
we never move from

01:11:58.210 --> 01:12:01.710 align:middle line:84%
this first little
two-bedroom house we live in,

01:12:01.710 --> 01:12:02.770 align:middle line:90%
I'm content with this.

01:12:02.770 --> 01:12:04.120 align:middle line:90%
I'm OK.

01:12:04.120 --> 01:12:06.200 align:middle line:90%
I'm just happy to be alive.

01:12:06.200 --> 01:12:09.030 align:middle line:84%
So everything else is
a bonus at this point.

01:12:09.030 --> 01:12:09.900 align:middle line:90%
I'm not dying.

01:12:09.900 --> 01:12:11.010 align:middle line:90%
I'm alive.

01:12:11.010 --> 01:12:12.480 align:middle line:90%
Great.

01:12:12.480 --> 01:12:16.440 align:middle line:84%
So I'm a little bit
of a unique case

01:12:16.440 --> 01:12:23.280 align:middle line:84%
because I had such a
dramatic karate chop, that--

01:12:23.280 --> 01:12:29.970 align:middle line:84%
