be thankful for every day.

01:13:18.660 --> 01:13:23.790 align:middle line:84%
Again, everything was
so hyper-clear to me.

01:13:23.790 --> 01:13:29.070 align:middle line:84%
I just had hyperclarity
in that time in my life

01:13:29.070 --> 01:13:32.690 align:middle line:84%
that it just basically
rewired my brain.

01:13:32.690 --> 01:13:36.210 align:middle line:84%
