contentment and gratitude.

01:13:36.210 --> 01:13:40.690 align:middle line:84%
And it dropped the bar
way down, way down.

01:13:40.690 --> 01:13:48.960 align:middle line:84%
And so now I'm 13 years out
and I'm still about the same.

01:13:48.960 --> 01:13:51.300 align:middle line:84%
There are days when
I can definitely

01:13:51.300 --> 01:13:54.660 align:middle line:84%
get grumpy and
irritated and annoyed

01:13:54.660 --> 01:13:57.020 align:middle line:90%
at things that don't matter.

01:13:57.020 --> 01:14:00.480 align:middle line:84%
And I have to catch
myself and be like,

01:14:00.480 --> 01:14:02.100 align:middle line:90%
