01:14:02.100 --> 01:14:03.150 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't matter.

01:14:03.150 --> 01:14:04.860 align:middle line:90%
It's fine.

01:14:04.860 --> 01:14:06.120 align:middle line:90%
It's irritating.

01:14:06.120 --> 01:14:08.410 align:middle line:90%
Let's forget about it.

01:14:08.410 --> 01:14:12.000 align:middle line:90%
And so I think--

01:14:12.000 --> 01:14:13.860 align:middle line:84%
I try to help people
understand this.

01:14:13.860 --> 01:14:16.080 align:middle line:84%
I try to remind people
of this, and especially

01:14:16.080 --> 01:14:17.070 align:middle line:90%
cancer patients, that--

01:14:17.070 --> 01:14:19.112 align:middle line:84%
