done on the happiest people

01:14:43.950 --> 01:14:44.750 align:middle line:90%
in the world.

01:14:44.750 --> 01:14:47.030 align:middle line:84%
And you Google it, it's
always the poorest cultures

01:14:47.030 --> 01:14:47.940 align:middle line:90%
